Gentlemen;

This month's OPORD for 25 APR 26 IDT is now available for your review,
comment, and edit.

Additionally, I expect that LTC Estes will visit at some point. Most likely
he will be present for the TNMAN-26 Ops Brief. For this brief, I will
require the ability to project  .pptx, .docx. and an .xlsx documents.

A FRAGO 26-05-01.1 (TNMAN) is being drafted for your consideration, and
these enclosures will be provided for you digitally at that time. I hope to
have that completed NLT Friday, APR 24.

Should you have any questions or concerns, please let me know.

-- 
V/R

JOHN T. SHEAF
LTC, TNSG
